@100 = ~Peacespeaker~
@101 = ~This crudely-crafted blade bears the mark of two unskilled apprentices. While the exterior is basic in form, and offers no hint to its power, trapped within lies the soul of a druid of Eldath. Occasionally, on a successful attack, the wielder may syphon part of her remaining powers - recovering a portion of their health.

Though lacking in raw offensive power, Peacespeaker offers powerful protective and healing magic.

STATISTICS:

Combat Ability:
– 40% chance per hit of casting Cure Medium Wounds on the wielder
– +20% resistance to slashing, piercing, and crushing damage

THAC0: +1
Damage: 1d8+1 (slashing)
Speed Factor: 4
Proficiency Type: Scimitar/Wakizashi/Ninjatō
Type: One-handed
Requires:
 6 Strength

Weight: 4~

