@104 = ~Bloodstained Grimoire~
@105 = ~This bloodstained spellbook stands as grim reminder that its wielder came to a gruesome end. Several of the pages within hold crudely scribed spells - many of them of beginner levels. Towards the end, however, the wielder starts to specialize in necromancy. Higher level spells of the particular school line the remaining pages. Along with increasingly erratic rants as the apprentice curses his mentor. Bemoaning his fate, since his mentor never has time to teach him and he's forced to experiment on his own. Often with less than desired results.

Several of the passages within should be of interest to Inspector Brega and assist him with further investigations.~

